Class Summary
Class Description
AbstractFrequencyTable
AbstractFrequencyTable used to define basic functionality that derived classes must implement
FrequencyTable
FrequencyTable used to store words and their frequency as key-value pairs, and perform operations on those key-value pairs
IgnoredWords
IgnoredWords used create list of words to be ignored, and check that a word is not in that list
Parser
Parser used to parse input into words and use those words to fill out frequency table
Runner
Runner used to run application and get input from user
WordCloud
WordCloud used to create a word-cloud image file with the words from the frequency table
